        <div class="test-info">
            <h3>Layout Test Features</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Two-column layout: Left (300px) for headers/footers, Right for content</li>
                <li>Sticky left column that follows scroll</li>
                <li>Mobile responsive: Single column on small screens</li>
                <li>Inline footnotes with superscript references</li>
                <li>Section headers highlighted in left column</li>
                <li>Max width capped to prevent overly wide layout</li>
